}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Requests a reload of weather conditions and forecast data from
enabled network services.
This call does no synchronous IO: rather, the result is delivered
by emitting the <link xref="GWeather.Info-updated"/> signal.
Note that if no network services are enabled, the signal will not
be emitted. See <link xref="GWeather.Info-enabled-providers"/> for details.</p>


